STATEWIDE INSURANCE FUND, as Subrogee of The County of Warren, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
OWL CONTRACTING, Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Daniel Hill, Third-Party Defendant-Respondent. C-531 September Term 2017
080226 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 26, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004669-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
